Siemens AG complies, and will continue to comply, with all the recommendations of the Government Commission on the German Corporate Governance Code in the version of April 28, 2022 (“Code”), pub lished by the Federal Ministry of Justice in the official section of the Federal Gazette ( Bundesanzeiger).

3. Information on corporate governance practices

Suggestions of the Code Siemens AG voluntarily complies with the Code’s sugges

tions, with only the following exception:

